-- Berkshire Furniture Unit Names Pederson CEO as Arnold Retires
-- B y   N o a h   B u h a y a r
-- 2012-06-26T14:28:30Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-26/berkshire-furniture-unit-names-pederson-ceo-as-arnold-retires.html
Berkshire Hathaway Inc. (BRK/A) ’s CORT
furniture-rental unit named Jeff Pederson as chief executive
officer, replacing Paul Arnold, who is stepping down after 40
years at the company, including two decades as CEO.  Pederson has served as president since 2006 and was
previously chief financial officer, according to a statement
today from Omaha, Nebraska-based Berkshire’s CORT unit.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Noah Buhayar in New York at 
 nbuhayar@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
